    <item>
      <title>在美国通胀出现关键性变化之前，黄金价格从新高回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/gold-retreats-as-robust-us-data-dampen-rate-cut-expectations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者将注意力转向本周晚些时候关键的美国通胀数据，金价在创下每盎司 2,350 美元新高后回吐涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/gold-retreats-as-robust-us-data-dampen-rate-cut-expectations</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 02:14:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油集会因以色列撤出部分加沙军队而暂停</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在以色列表示将从加沙撤走部分军队后，油价跌破每桶90美元，由于地缘政治摩擦显示出缓和迹象，原油近期的涨势目前面临技术阻力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 23:26:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
